entry.title: JKM White & Natural Bias Tape Fabric - 60" Width
entry.summary:
Vendor: JKM
Type: Fabric
Price: 128.26 - 650.97 (8 variants)

Our white & natural bias tape fabric comes in the following sizes: 60" width on 10, 25, 50 & 100 yard bolts. Note: The same Fabric and colors used to make JKM Bias Tape is available to compliment your purchase of JKM bias tape, to make your own bias tape or to use for any of your project needs. This Fabric is available in 4 roll sizes: 10 yards, 25 yards, 50 yards or 100 yards. All rolls are 60 inches wide. Please note that these fabrics come with a firm finish since they are used in Bias Tape production. The fabric will soften with washing.JKM will only ship these rolls by UPS Ground due to freight limitations. When you checkout, please use the UPS Ground option. Also, view the complementary bias tape and view the complementary piping.
(Product Characteristic: Fabric Bolt-Solid;Print) / (Fabric Content: 50% Polyester 50% Cotton)
